         <abstract id="aspace_a8b837d43f6a96f94c1dc489dceb66d4">Papers of the family of Agur Gilbert, wood turners and toy makers of Derby, Connecticut. Consists of family correspondence, business letters, and account books, primarily for A. Gilbert and Son.</abstract>
